      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and shows signs of regular use consistent with its age. While it remains a reliable daily driver, there are several cosmetic imperfections, including some noticeable scratches on the passenger side doors and fading paint on the roof. Mechanically, the engine starts and runs fine, though the suspension is starting to feel a bit loose and may require servicing in the near future. The interior is clean but shows wear on the driver's seat and some minor staining on the rear carpets. It\u2019s a solid option for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming maintenance.",
