    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six and a precise 6-speed manual gearbox. This driver-spec example boasts a linear power delivery via individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The subframe has been inspected for structural integrity, and the double-VANOS system operates smoothly. While showing honest patina consistent with its age, the suspension geometry remains tight, offering the visceral feedback this chassis is renowned for. A perfect acquisition for the purist seeking an analog driving experience.",
