    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained 2018 executive sedan that strikes a perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the passenger-side mirror housing, consistent with careful daily use. The alloy wheels are free of curb rash and are wrapped in tires with plenty of life left. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the leather seats are soft and intact, showing only light natural softening on the driver's seat. All interior electronics, including the touchscreen interface, heated seats, and sunroof, operate exactly as they should. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and provides smooth, consistent power. I have adhered to a strict maintenance schedule, including recent fluid flushes and a fresh oil change. The car tracks straight, brakes firmly without pulsing, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This vehicle comes with two sets of keys, the original owner\u2019s manuals, and a clean title. It is a dependable, high-quality choice for anyone seeking a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
